ac{1}{1-x}$ ，\n根据反比例函数 $y=\\frac{1}{-x}$ 的平移可得到 $f(x)$ ，则此时 $f(x)$ 单调递增, 作出图像如下图所示,\n\n第二步:\n令\n\n$$\ng(x)=f(x)-m x+\\frac{2}{3} m=0\n$$\n\n即\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_10_24_47a253f79e08acf28419g-26.jpg?height=429&width=577&top_left_y=314&top_left_x=1342","line":526}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"3nne2h","at":1771320836536}},"smart_blocks:01-数学教学/试卷/10-试卷汇总/试卷 md 版本/功底考16题1-16套.md#科目二答题示例": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.04991288,0.01267606,0.03342852,-0.06160135,0.01144101,0.00855273,-0.00706956,-0.01949437,0.01618934,-0.00512286,0.02309576,-0.03480772,0.03518052,0.0018203,0.01848196,0.03199476,-0.03265546,-0.03255492,-0.04625231,-0.00147514,0.13965018,-0.04753455,0.00159538,-0.06687325,0.03779567,0.03954517,0.03449601,-0.0404774,0.01537481,-0.19625986,0.0021838,0.02261583,0.00293345,0.03122753,0.03409331,-0.0489203,-0.00223526,0.06657884,-0.072458,0.04178528,-0.00024542,0.06490517,0.05457823,-0.02414131,0.02504973,-0.02890713,-0.0234721,-0.03467819,0.0324563,-0.04641665,-0.05696785,-0.02636158,-0.02000139,0.03429027,0.01177609,0.00312582,0.00124647,0.06601211,0.00537535,-0.02769022,0.03175558,0.03416535,-0.24300735,0.02555292,0.06220577,-0.02290839,-0.00098991,-0.02269677,0.06334428,0.08151231,-0.04457114,0.00682502,0.01970654,0.03978351,-0.00250017,0.00598163,0.03787119,-0.01447782,-0.04366069,-0.04574795,-0.01591371,0.07386746,0.04028086,-0.01811812,-0.00599239,0.00916768,0.01052374,-0.08870983,-0.01724162,-0.05000269,-0.00572362,-0.01851952,-0.00018443,0.05321404,-0.0470432,0.01384031,0.01254404,0.03439578,-0.02008414,0.10664137,-0.04414664,0.08683872,0.004166,-0.07268767,0.00708394,-0.04195653,-0.02108748,-0.09332753,-0.02016859,-0.02628477,-0.03058165,-0.02119832,0.07882762,-0.06860735,-0.01208822,-0.01445339,0.0840414,0.0219694,-0.02740637,-0.00882301,0.02283633,0.04991294,0.0308283,-0.04241117,-0.00154392,-0.07540068,0.02305821,0.00966171,0.04531051,0.05021164